==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rheumy
<hw>Rheum"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
rheum; abounding in, or causing, rheum; affected with rheum.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His head and <qex>rheumy</qex> eyes distill in showers.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And tempt the <qex>rheumy</qex> and unpurged air⟦br⟧
To add unto his sickness.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rhigolene</ent>⟦br⟧
